title: Tai Ngao Jan
overview: Satayu, a businessman from the powerful Sasiwong family, never knew love until he met Paboo, a young woman raised in a broken home and spoiled by money, making her selfish and fickle. Her new position at Sasiwong Group is a test for her. She has to work with Satayu and Buri, a warm-hearted architect from a modest but loving family. Paboo forms bonds with both men. In the end, who will win her heart?
